query: SELECT fl.id, fl.centreId, fl.levelName, fl.levelNumber, fl.isHidden, sc.name as centreName FROM floor_levels fl JOIN shopping_centres sc ON fl.centreId = sc.id WHERE fl.isHidden = 1;
